  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forest Asylum is a psychological horror experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your way through an abandoned mental asylum and find out what brought you here and what the goal of this journey is. Discover the dark secret that lies behind the rooms deep in the dark basement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512200/extras/f07135f597e0a4c5f1440bad3820a1a9.avif?t=1752147148\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512200/extras_big/f07135f597e0a4c5f1440bad3820a1a9.avif?t=1752147148 width=800 height=536 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to do your work to escape from the asylum. Solve puzzles to progress further in the story and find out what happened in the forest mental asylum - because you didn't end up there by accident or did you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512200/extras/5f27d377da253a5cecdcc310cb8d4692.avif?t=1752147148\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512200/extras_big/5f27d377da253a5cecdcc310cb8d4692.avif?t=1752147148 width=800 height=536 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thrilling Story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychological Horror</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse and smart puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A job to do</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short experience for one evening (30-60 minutes of gameplay)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story told via old images (knowledge of English is not necessary)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forest Asylum is a psychological horror experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your way through an abandoned mental asylum and find out what brought you here and what the goal of this journey is. Discover the dark secret that lies behind the rooms deep in the dark basement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512200/extras/f07135f597e0a4c5f1440bad3820a1a9.avif?t=1752147148\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512200/extras_big/f07135f597e0a4c5f1440bad3820a1a9.avif?t=1752147148 width=800 height=536 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to do your work to escape from the asylum. Solve puzzles to progress further in the story and find out what happened in the forest mental asylum - because you didn't end up there by accident or did you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512200/extras/5f27d377da253a5cecdcc310cb8d4692.avif?t=1752147148\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512200/extras_big/5f27d377da253a5cecdcc310cb8d4692.avif?t=1752147148 width=800 height=536 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thrilling Story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychological Horror</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse and smart puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A job to do</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short experience for one evening (30-60 minutes of gameplay)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story told via old images (knowledge of English is not necessary)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
